      "span_text": "The tool takes the following steps: 1) Decompilation: Given an APK file, the tool first decompiles the app using the command line version of the JADX decompilation tool. [CITATION_1] A successful decompilation will provide us with a project folder that contains decompiled Java source code of the app and the resource files.",
